# Sales / demo decks — never commit binary .pptx into the repo
# (HuggingFace's xet/LFS pre-receive hook scans full history;
# a stray .pptx blocks every subsequent Space deploy until the
# history is scrubbed with git filter-repo).
decks/
*.pptx

